cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with image classification using deep learning architectures and graph-based representations, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The specific focus on omnidirectional cameras also suggests a potential fit for the graphics (cs.GR) category. Additionally, the use of graph-based representations and deep learning techniques suggests a potential fit for artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories.
